title: Let's Pui Pui Molcar! :: Switch Game based on TV Series

media:group.media:title: Let's Pui Pui Molcar! :: Switch Game based on TV Series
media:group.media:description:
Featuring the adorable guinea pigs from the crazy popular Japanese TV show Pui Pui Molcar.
The game is suitable for smaller children.
I bought my copy from PlayAsia.

14:50 Vroom vroom!
